Defendant Sylvia M Taylor in court with attorney William Robert Kerner.   Kristi Gordon appeared for the State of Wisconsin.    The Defendant was given the following:

Count 5:
WITHHELD SENTENCE;

TERM OF PROBATION:  2 YEAR(S);

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:   (same as listed in 15CF105)
AODA assessment and follow through with any treatment/counseling. Maintain absolute sobriety. Random U.A.'s..   Follow thru with any treatment/counseling recommended by Agent. No use or possession of alcohol or controlled substances without a valid prescription. No drug paraphernalia. Any valid prescription drugs must be taken only in the manner in which they are prescribed; Inform Agent of all prescriptions. Maintain full-time employment and/or combination of schooling.  No association with known drug users or dealers and no contact at any place where illegal drugs are purchased, used, stored, packaged or distributed.   Defendant to provide DNA sample, if not yet provided, immediately if in custody otherwise within (3) business days at the Waukesha County Sheriff Department. 
*Perform 60 Hours Community Service. 

COURT COSTS:  $268.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $250.00 (to be paid as a condition of probation);

CONDITION TIME: 12 MONTHS (CONCURRENT TO 15CF105) TIME SERVED. 

Felony warnings, voting rights and firearms warnings given.
